Did this flawless skin look using @marcbeauty re(marc)able foundation and I didn’t retouch the image at all - nothing, not even the brightness - zoom right in to see how this foundation looks in HQ! A little bit of this foundation goes a long way (if you know, you know 👀😉) and the result is a radiant, matte & flawless finish! I used the shade ‘beige 34’ from @sephoraaus #marcfam #sephoraaus #remarcablefoundation

My husband surprised me with a bouquet of flowers and it elevated my perfume shoot to something way cuter 🌸🌸🌸 this is the latest fragrance from @elizabetharden, My Fifth Avenue - It’s fresh & floral, so perfect for spring/summer 💕 the spirit of NYC in a bottle! Would make a divine gift under the tree 🤩 who’s had a chance to smell #myfifthavenue? #elizabethardenau

@sebamecha and I are supporting @poloralphlauren #pinkpony this year, because 100% of each sale of these cute #poloralphlauren Live/Love graphic tees goes toward fighting cancer. My beloved Aunty Joan passed away from breast cancer, my grandmother survived it and you might remember that my close friend also beat a brain tumour. The Pink Pony campaign supports programs for screening, early diagnosis, treatment, education and patient navigation. They’re on sale now and not only do they support the cause but they look so cute, and if you can’t buy a top, feel free to drop a comment and a like to get this post out there! Xx Chlo & seba

glitter gloss OBSESSED and this one from the #marcbeauty holiday collection is no exception! It’s the @MarcBeauty Enamored Hi-Shine Gloss Lip Lacquer in 'Shine a Light' - it has gold & pink glimmers, looks as shiny as 30 coats of laquer, makes my lips look huge and glossy but somehow isnt sticky whatsoever! I personally love gloss worn alone but it also looks divine over lipstick!! Who wants one in their Christmas stocking this year? 👋👋#marcfam #marcjacobsbeauty #marcholiday #sephoraaus @sephoraaus
